Package org.treetank Description

Root package for all packages. This includes:

  • access: Direct access layer for interaction with treetank
  • api: Interfaces for offering abstract implementations
  • axis: Different Axis for tree iterations
  • cache: Caching and transaction log classes
  • exception: Exception classes
  • io: classes for writing data to the disk
  • node: Nodelayer, all nodes are represented by this classes
  • page: Pagelayer, all revisions which are storing nodes are represented by these classes
  • service: XML + meta structures
  • settings: constant variables are defined over here
  • util: the rest, what else.

Author:
Sebastian Graf, University of Konstanz
